text: Cooling is the transfer of thermal energy via thermal radiation, heat conduction or convection. Cooling may also refer to: *Cooling (surname), any of several people *"Cooling", a song written and performed by Tori Amos on her 1999 album To Venus and Back * A nickname of the town of Guling, Jiangxi, China * Cooling, Kent, a village in Kent, England
title: Cooling (disambiguation)
